snippet.title: WEB3WAR – Multiplayer Map Demo: The Containers
snippet.description:
Check out the latest live demonstration of #WEB3WAR - a first-person shooter game currently being developed in-house by #Zilliqa - featuring multiplayer map The Containers. 

Keen to get hands-on with WEB3WAR and test it out for yourself before anyone else? Join our Discord for information on how to take part in our beta testing rounds, starting October 7, 2022, at: http://discord.gg/web3war
